snippet.title: Bombball Trailer (OUYA)
snippet.description:
http://www.emcneill.com/bombball/

Bombball is an explosive sports game, available now on the OUYA console. Bombball is designed to be spectator-friendly and easy to learn, while still requiring real skill to master.
